Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,LEARN. Cognitive-development analytics for USMC schoolhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: Learning Intelligence Dashboard. Are Marines actually\Nlearning?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen students. Six assignments. Two hundred forum posts. One\Nquestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Synthetic Moodle export streams in. No data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A three-stage agent scores every student against the USMC competency\Nrubric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts the Instructors Competency Brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-click drill-down: heatmap to student to remediation\Nrecommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Class-level competency map. Top performers. Intervention list.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Every assessment SHA-256 chained. SJA, IG, and TRADOC can replay\Nmonths later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. FERPA-friendly. IL5 ready. Deploy in\Nhours.
